application

Class GUIController

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.GUIController

  • public class GUIController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class controls all of the functionality that occurs within our Student Database application. This is known as the controller class where a TableView is used in replacement of a JTable.
    Author:
    William Shreeve, Hai Duong, and Trung-vuong Pham
